[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Kai asked me several questions as we rush our way to the emergency room with Lan.[p]
Tears suddenly flow down from my eyes. Kai look at me with shock.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
[layopt layer=message1 visible=false]
[layopt layer=message0 visible=true]

[current layer="message0"]
[_tb_end_tyrano_code]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
Are you...crying now?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
[layopt layer=message1 visible=true]
[layopt layer=message0 visible=false]

[current layer="message1"]
[_tb_end_tyrano_code]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
He then angrily said[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
[layopt layer=message1 visible=false]
[layopt layer=message0 visible=true]

[current layer="message0"]
[_tb_end_tyrano_code]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
Get out of the operation room! Get out of the operation room! Get me a new nurse, this one is unusable![p]
Get me a new nurse, this one is unusable![p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
[layopt layer=message1 visible=true]
[layopt layer=message0 visible=false]

[current layer="message1"]
[_tb_end_tyrano_code]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Just like that they lock me out of the emergency room. Wiping tears of my face, i get angry of myself.[p]
It was so unprofessional of me. I come back to work, carrying on with my tasks. But i couldn't get Lan out of my head. [p]
Every now and then, i come back to emergency room's doors to check if the operation is finished. [p]
5 hours later, i see Kai talking to Minh. Lan's boyfriend looks at Kai with tears in his eyes and nods his head repeatedly to say thank you.[p]
After Kai finishes talking, i come to ask him[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
[layopt layer=message1 visible=false]
[layopt layer=message0 visible=true]

[current layer="message0"]
[_tb_end_tyrano_code]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
What happened? Is Lan ok now?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
The operation was successful.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
Thanks God...thanks God she's ok now.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
[layopt layer=message1 visible=true]
[layopt layer=message0 visible=false]

[current layer="message1"]
[_tb_end_tyrano_code]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
I burst out crying. I was praying for her all day.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
[layopt layer=message1 visible=false]
[layopt layer=message0 visible=true]

[current layer="message0"]
[_tb_end_tyrano_code]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
God didn't save her. I did.[p]
And we have to talk about that crying nature of yours. Just what exactly did you even think?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
I'm so sorry..[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
Within this job you aren't allowed to look panic or helpless because that will make the patient panic too.[p]
You had to be the place for them to lean on, especially in dangerous situations[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
I'm sorry... I just...i can't help it.[p]
She's a friend of mine. I know how hard she's been fighting, i know how hard did it take for her to get here. This tumor can end her dream as a chef or even her life.[p]
When i think about it i just couldn't help but worry[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
[layopt layer=message1 visible=true]
[layopt layer=message0 visible=false]

[current layer="message1"]
[_tb_end_tyrano_code]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
I try so hard to wipe the tears off but my eyes betray me. Kai leaves out a big sigh then pulls me into his chest and pats my head. Just like that, i keep crying[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
From behind the doors, Lan sees it all. She watches both of them and smiles warmly[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
The next day[p]
[_tb_end_text]

