[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Lan
Hey you know, Minh and i are about to get married[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
Congrats!!! I know you two love birds will have this day!![p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Lan
Yeah! We grow up in the same orphanage together.[p]
Dreamed of opening a restaurant and having a family together. And after so many years of working so hard to get it, we'll finally have our dreams come true. [p]
Isn't that wonderful? Cancer might have taken a lot of things away from me but in the end i will win, just you see![p]
[_tb_end_text]

